The '''Ice Boat''' (or Ocean Ice) is a [[Floating Platform]] that spawns after an [[Ice Floe]] collapses. It will slowly lose health at a rate of -2 {{Hull}}/s and drops 3 [[Ice/DST|Ice]] once its health reaches 0 and leaves behind some visual small pieces of ice on water.

